General.Name: Ozderici Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi AS
General.Description: Ozderici Gayrimenkul Yatirim Ortakligi A.S. operates as a real estate investment trust in Turkey. It designs projects in the real estate property sector in the areas of land improvement, project design, and urban transformation, as well as focuses on the housing sector. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
